# Xcode / Swift .gitignore
# Based on github/gitignore Swift + Xcode templates

## User settings & state
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Build artifacts
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

# NOTE: The project is Xcode-managed and committed (see README). We still ignore
# per-user state below; only the shared project structure is tracked.

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/

## CocoaPods / Carthage (unused, but ignore if added later)
Pods/
Carthage/Build/

## Editor / tooling local state
.claude/

## macOS
.DS_Store

## Misc
*.swp
*.save

## Markdown — keep only README.md tracked. Other .md files are local
## reference notes (spec, scratchpads) and should stay out of the repo.
*.md
!README.md
